      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:47:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国央行称德国第一季度GDP可能增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/german-economy-probably-grew-in-first-quarter-bundesbank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国经济——欧洲最大的——德国央行表示，由于年初制造业回升、出口增加和建筑业激增，德国经济有望避免冬季衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/german-economy-probably-grew-in-first-quarter-bundesbank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
